# User Story

AS AN alternative fuel source vehicle owner
I WANT to find the location of alternative fuel sources
SO THAT I can keep driving

# Acceptance Criteria

GIVEN a map with fuel locators
WHEN I search for fuel locations
THEN I'm presented with a list of locations
WHEN I switch to map view 
THEN I am presented with markers on my map

